		<title>2024 Presidential Election: How Trump or Harris&#8217;s Victory Could Shape Financial Markets and Create Trading Opportunities</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en-ae/analysis/trading-strategies/trump-vs-harris-election-market-impact-2024</link>
		
